### Genfeed API - HeyGen Integration Endpoints
### Manage HeyGen AI avatar videos
### Handles: avatar videos, voice cloning

########################################
# Video Generation
########################################

### Generate Avatar Video
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/heygen/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avatarId": "{{heygenAvatarId}}",
  "voiceId": "{{heygenVoiceId}}",
  "text": "Welcome to our presentation"
}


### Check Generation Status
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/heygen/status/{{generationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Avatars
########################################

### Get Available Avatars
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/heygen/avatars
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Voices
########################################

### Get Available Voices
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/heygen/voices
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Invalid Generation ID
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/heygen/status/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/heygen/generate
